---
title: KW Ruby Developers
---
- require_relative '../lib/meetup_feed'

%section.hero
  .side-image
    .side-image-content
      .hero__flex-wrapper
        .hero__flex-left
          %i.devicon-ruby-plain
        .hero__flex-right
          %h1.hero__title
            Dedicated to learning and sharing about <a href='http://ruby-lang.org'>Ruby</a>
          %h2#skill
            All skill levels are welcome.
          %h3
            We meet once a month for a workshop, training session, or discussion.
          %form(action='http://www.meetup.com/kw-ruby-on-rails/')
            %input{type: 'submit', value: 'Join us!', class: 'hero__link'}

%section.container
  %ul.bullets
    = partial(:meeting_bullet, locals: {events: MeetupFeed.upcoming_meetings})

    %li.bullet
      .bullet-icon.bullet-icon-3
      .bullet-content
        %h2 Our Wiki
        %p
          %a(href='/wiki'){id: 'wiki-link'}
            Wiki
